        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;概述overview&#34;&gt;概述|Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Python, created by Guido van Rossum in 1989, was named after his favorite comedy troupe, Monty Python.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, Python is a major programming language. It is used in web development, database administration, and AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most importantly to GIS Analysts, Python can be used to control ArcGIS tools and Map Documents to produce geospatial data and maps in an organized and speedy manner using the excellent ArcPy module.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;python的特点&#34;&gt;Python的特点&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;简单易学&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;免费且开源&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;跨平台&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;arcgis-和-python&#34;&gt;ArcGIS 和 Python&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ArcGIS for Desktop 支持使用脚本语言实现任务自动化.Python是ArcGIS首选的脚本语言&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Python 脚本可以像常见的地理处理工具一样，变成一个脚本工具，直接整合到 ArcGIS 中。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ArcGIS  10 安装后自带一个 Python 2.7&lt;/p&gt;
